data.description: Hurry! Don't miss your chance to own this gorgeous home in desirable Brentwood Lakes gated community. This 4 bed 2.5 bath home is situated on .2 acres in of 1 of the 2 cul-de-sacs in the community! This home has modern upgrades, fresh paint and tile throughout. Tons of counterspace and cabinets in the kitchen along with an island/breakfast bar, SS appliances & an oversized pantry! Perfect for entertaining!  Master bedroom is on the 1st floor for extra privacy! Upstairs you will find a huge loft/bonus room, 3 additional bedrooms w/walk in closets and a bathroom with tub/shower. Enjoy your large back yard anytime of the year with your paved patio and firepit! Brand new roof October 2023 and newer AC. Outdoor security camera system with hi-res video's/pictures. Hurry! this won't last long!  Seller offering buyer incentives.
